<div class="about-page">
  <h1>About AI Reviews</h1>
  
  <section class="about-section">
    <h2>Our Mission</h2>
    <p>AI Reviews is dedicated to providing objective, professional, and comprehensive evaluations of AI tools. In this rapidly evolving AI landscape, we aim to help individuals and businesses find the most suitable AI solutions for their needs, avoiding confusion among the many options available.</p>
  </section>
  
  <section class="about-section">
    <h2>Our Evaluation Criteria</h2>
    <p>Each review article is based on a thorough analysis using the following criteria:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Feature Completeness:</strong> Does the tool provide sufficient functionality to fulfill its stated purpose</li>
      <li><strong>Usability:</strong> Interface design, learning curve, and user experience</li>
      <li><strong>Performance & Efficiency:</strong> Speed, accuracy, and resource usage</li>
      <li><strong>Pricing & Value:</strong> Analysis of different pricing plans and their value proposition</li>
      <li><strong>Support & Documentation:</strong> Quality of customer support and documentation completeness</li>
      <li><strong>Security & Privacy:</strong> Data handling and privacy protection measures</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
  
  <section class="about-section">
    <h2>Rating System</h2>
    <p>We use a 5-star rating system, evaluating each tool in the following areas:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Features (25%)</strong></li>
      <li><strong>Usability (20%)</strong></li>
      <li><strong>Performance (20%)</strong></li>
      <li><strong>Pricing (20%)</strong></li>
      <li><strong>Support (15%)</strong></li>
    </ul>
    <p>The final score is a weighted average of these categories, rounded to the nearest half-star.</p>
  </section>
  
  <section class="about-section">
    <h2>Our Commitment</h2>
    <p>We commit to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Personally testing every tool we review</li>
      <li>Providing objective, unbiased evaluations</li>
      <li>Clearly labeling any sponsored content</li>
      <li>Regularly updating our reviews to reflect the latest changes</li>
      <li>Listening to reader feedback and continuously improving</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
  
